        <p style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 40px;">FolioWeave is built on the understanding that cultural friction is often invisible until it’s too late. Subtle differences in **fashion, communication, and storytelling** can lead to misunderstandings, lost opportunities, and even offense.</p>

        <div class="faux-pas-grid">
            <div id="card-fashion" class="faux-pas-card">
                <h4>Fashion Faux Pas</h4>
                <p style="font-weight: 600;">Image Placeholder: Dress with a misused sacred motif.</p>
                <p style="font-style: italic; color: #666;">(Click/Hover to Reveal FolioWeave Insight)</p>
                <div class="insight-reveal">
                    **FolioWeave Insight:** **We'd flag this.** The **Naga symbol** (a mythical serpent revered across Southeast Asia) is sacred; placing it here and using it for mass production is deeply offensive to certain communities.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="card-comm" class="faux-pas-card">
                <h4>Communication Breakdown</h4>
                <p style="font-weight: 600;">Image Placeholder: Confused business meeting.</p>
                <p style="font-style: italic; color: #666;">(Click/Hover to Reveal FolioWeave Insight)</p>
                <div class="insight-reveal">
                    **FolioWeave Insight:** **A clear 'no' was never heard.** An indirect 'yes, but...' from an ASEAN partner was mistaken for agreement. FolioWeave decodes the unspoken 'yes, but...' for high-context cultures.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="card-folklore" class="faux-pas-card">
                <h4>Folklore Mismatch</h4>
                <p style="font-weight: 600;">Image Placeholder: Logo using a rooster awkwardly.</p>
                <p style="font-style: italic; color: #666;">(Click/Hover to Reveal FolioWeave Insight)</p>
                <div class="insight-reveal">
                    **FolioWeave Insight:** **Lack of a deeper narrative.** FolioWeave connects the French **Gallic Rooster** to the Philippine **Sarimanok**, inspiring a more profound, shared narrative of vigilance and pride.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
