                        <li><span class="context-label" style="color: var(--color-earth);">ASEAN Context:</span> Prioritize rapport-building, not immediate business. The first 30 minutes are for getting to know the person. Avoid aggressive sales pitches.</li>
                        <li><span class="context-label" style="color: var(--color-indigo);">French Context:</span> Be prepared for intellectual debate; they value logic and critical thinking. Direct discussion of the project is expected after initial pleasantries.</li>
                        <li><span class="context-label" style="color: var(--color-gold);">Bridging Phrase:</span> "I'd like to understand the reasoning behind that perspective. It will help ensure our team can deliver in a way that aligns with your expectations." (Respectful, direct, and process-focused.)</li>
